<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一位艺术家<delay20 />
对其作品倾注生命，<delay20 />
这样的工作真是了不起<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样被创造出的古老作品<delay20 />存续至今，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为人们带来感动，一想到这里，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就觉得这实在非常厉害。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />艺术是用心感受之物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以它的门槛并不高。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也抱着轻松愉快的心来观赏就好。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />虽然说得很内行，<delay20 />
但其实我也不是很懂。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈！</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />了解作者的意图和时代背景之后，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能更陶醉地欣赏艺术。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过最重要的还是自己感受艺术的心。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果下次还有机会，希望我们能好好地<delay20 />
聊一聊彼此喜欢的作品。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有好好欣赏<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="8" />的艺术品吗？<10_4 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请继续慢慢观赏。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你对艺术有兴趣吗？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实我对艺术非常着迷。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我和你似乎很合得来……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />艺术告诉了我，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />世上是没有极限的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们拥有无尽的自由<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我希望你也能从这里的艺术之中<delay20 />
领会到一些事物。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到有一天竟能在<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />
与艺术亲密接触～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后能欣赏到怎样的作品呢？<delay20 />
我实在太期待了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才刚刚开门，<delay20 />
展示空间都还没有放满<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在作品足够多之前，不如把我放上去展示吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />开玩笑的，<delay20 />哈哈！</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实，<delay20 />我暗地里梦想过，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望在<tag a="110" b="8" />上<delay20 />　
能建设出这样的空间。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到真的会实现。<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，下一个梦想就是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个空间里能充满艺术。</message>
